RockEncantech Store

RockEncantech Store is a full-stack e-commerce catalog application built as a technical challenge.
It includes a Laravel backend API and a React frontend, fully containerized with Docker.

🚀 Features

Backend (Laravel)

User registration and login

Token-based authentication with Laravel Sanctum

Product listing with pagination

Product search (name & description)

Category filtering

Product details endpoint

Protected CRUD operations

Categories endpoint

Validation (unique email, strong password)

Service Layer + Repository Pattern

API Resources for standardized responses

Frontend (React)

Product listing page

Product cards (name, description, price, image, category)

Search functionality

Category filter

Pagination

Product details page

Login and Register pages

Token stored in localStorage

Authenticated API requests using Axios

Navigation with React Router

UI built with Material UI

